      <title>理解 Linux Kernel (7) - 字符设备</title>
      <link>https://www.ffutop.com/2018/12/28/%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3-linux-kernel-7-%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87/</link>
